description:
StarTrek: The Next Generation Music
Inner Light - Jay Chattaway


Information:
This Instrumental Song referred as a &quot;old folk melody&quot; from Ressikan by Captain Picard in Episode 19 Season 6: Lessons, was first heard in Episode 25 Season 5: The Inner Light from which the song's name is derived.

More on both episodes can be found on Wikipedia here:
