Uploader's Comments:

Those episodes as well as this song received high praise from fans, and the episode: inner Light 5x25 won the Hugo Award for best dramatic presentation. I highlight that from Wikipedia to show that I am not the only person moved by this song, and these episodes. 

As such I wanted to make this song more widely available, as I had to search extensively just to find it. I don't believe this to breaking any copy write laws as the song can be found at:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.themusichutch.com/listen.php?songid=10903&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.themusichutch.com/listen.php?songid=10903&lt;/a&gt;

I just recorded it, and put it into MP3 format for ease of use. 

The Orchestra version can be found here:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://beemp3.com/download.php?file=7743197&amp;song=Orchestral+Suite+from+the+Inner+Light&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://beemp3.com/download.php?file=7743197&amp;song=Orchestral+Suite+from+the+Inner+Light&lt;/a&gt;

However there are intermitant high pitched beeps which ruins it.

Enjoy! and please seed at least a 1:1 ratio...
